description:
&lt;p&gt;Are you a NHS 111 Pathways Trained Clinical Advisor who is passionate about making a difference to patients? &lt;strong&gt;If so, we are offering a £1,500 GOLDEN HELLO bonus for joining our team! &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Practice Plus Group are looking for NHS 111 Pathways Trained Clinical Advisors to join our busy 111 Call Centre in Stoke Gifford, Bristol.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We have numerous shift patterns available, ranging from 16 – 38.5 hours per week. These patterns are on a 2-8 week rota and include daytime, evenings, nights and weekend working so we should be able to offer you something that fits in with your lifestyle.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;We can offer: &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;• &lt;strong&gt;Hourly rate:&lt;/strong&gt; £19.81 if you work between 07:00-22:59 and £22.52 if you work between 23:00-06:59&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;• £1500 bonus after you have successfully completed 6 months of probation.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;In addition to the above pay rates, we also offer:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;•Further pay enhancements for some of our busier shifts *T&amp;Cs apply&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;•33 days annual leave (pro-rata, including bank holidays)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;•Company Pension Scheme&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;•2x Life Assurance&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;•Contribution towards Eye test and Glasses&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;•Cycle to work scheme – offering discounts rates and payment plans of bicycles and equipment&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;•Practice Plus Group perks –offering you discounts and cash back with large retailers&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;•Annual employee recognition award ceremony&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;•Career development opportunities&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;•Access to our bespoke e-learning system&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;To be considered for this role you will need to fulfil the following criteria:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;• You must hold a full nursing or paramedic qualification, and be registered with the NMC or HCPC&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;• You are currently working on the 111 service in the role of Clinical Advisor, or have done so within the last six months&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;• You must be trained up to the latest version of Pathways&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;£1,500 GOLDEN HELLO Terms and conditions apply&lt;/p&gt;
